  Source: actual_theme/templates/error_page.hbs

  REMOVED FROM COPENHAGEN:
  - container-divider and error-page id="main-content"

  ADDED FROM PRODUCTION:
  - Custom search section with "Page not found..." heading (c-simple-search)
  - Standard error handling (oops, unauthorized, forbidden, not_found)
  - Back to homepage link
